cal Veterans Administra tor Wilmington Contract office last night reported that since Janu arv i over 750000 insurance has been reinstated and converted to permanent policies The announcement came on the fve of the day and night confer ence scheduled to start this morn jng at 11 oclock in the Community Council chambers fourth floor fide Water building E C Baker regional insurance officer for the VA WinstonSalem jtivcd yesterday afternoon to at tend the conference and make an inspection of the local set up He said yesterday afternoon that the local office was the first in the state to keep daily records on veterans insurance accounts Invited to attend the meeting this JXJTLOOK FOR GEORGIA PEACHES Quantity of Georgia Peach Crop Harvested Each Year Each Bushel Equals 1000000 Bushels of Peaches 1946 Est 1945 1944 1943 1942 6580000 8091000 4590000 1593000 6177000 TK morning are representatives of all local insurance companies and all members of the legion and its af filiate organizations Baker is here to get Information concerning the local contract of fice work with government insur ance"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-08-12T17:36:31.033Z", "group": ["ndnp/ncu", "university-of-north-carolina-chapel-hill-library-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn78002169/1946-05-31/ed-1/?sp=5", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ncu:batch_ncu_iris_ver01:data:sn78002169:0027955890A:1946053101:0383/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=418&w=314", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ncu:batch_ncu_iris_ver01:data:sn78002169:0027955890A:1946053101:0383/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=837&w=628", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ncu/batch_ncu_iris_ver01/data/sn78002169/0027955890A/1946053101/0383.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["new hanover county", "united states", "new hanover", "north carolina", "wilmingto